 his father's administration.</i>

00:00:19.218 --> 00:00:21.654 line:0%
So with the destroy Trump media
floating baseless

00:00:21.687 --> 00:00:24.557 line:0%
Russia conspiracy theories
every second of every day,

00:00:24.590 --> 00:00:26.759 line:0%
and of course,
Democrats on Capitol Hill

00:00:26.792 --> 00:00:29.896 line:0%
desperately searching for any
evidence of collusion,

00:00:29.929 --> 00:00:31.831 line:0%
well, President Trump's sons,

00:00:31.864 --> 00:00:33.433 line:0%
they are now coming
to his defense.

00:00:33.466 --> 00:00:34.967 line:0%
Joining us now,
the man himself,

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.303 line:0%
executive vice president
of the Trump Organization.

00:00:37.336 --> 00:00:38.838 line:0%
I've never seen hatred
like this.

00:00:38.871 --> 00:00:40.473 line:0%
I mean, to me they're not
even people.

00:00:40.506 --> 00:00:41.908 line:0%
It's-it's so, so sad.

00:00:41.941 --> 00:00:44.410 line:0%
I mean, morality's just gone.

00:00:44.443 --> 00:00:46.212 line:0%
Um, morals have flown out
the window.

00:00:46.245 --> 00:00:50.049
Wow. Wow.

00:00:50.082 --> 00:00:53.953
The same guy, the same guy
who got so upset

00:00:53.986 --> 00:00:56.756
when Hillary called his dad's
supporters "deplorables,"

00:00:56.789 --> 00:00:59.725
