aren't even human beings?

00:00:59.758 --> 00:01:02.328
Really? And he didn't even warm
up to it in the interview.

00:01:02.361 --> 00:01:04.430
It was practically the first
thing out of his mouth.

00:01:04.463 --> 00:01:07.266
