00:02:15.167 --> 00:02:18.404
That is--
I mean, that is just...

00:02:18.437 --> 00:02:19.839
So, so sad.

00:02:19.872 --> 00:02:22.074
I mean, morality's just gone.

00:02:22.107 --> 00:02:24.844
Morals have flown out
the window.

00:02:24.877 --> 00:02:27.446
My man.

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:30.316
(laughter and applause)

